snippet.title: The Rule of Land Pioneers trailer [ENG]
snippet.description: This is a survival game. After the coronation, human beings had to move into the underground. Fifty years later, some people thought the disaster was over and organized a survival competition on the surface. Some brave people took part in the competition . You are one of them.
